data.description: Modern and well-maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom single-story home built in 2006. This property features a fresh coat of new paint, offering a clean and inviting atmosphere. With a functional one-story layout, it provides ease of living and convenience. Ideal for those seeking a contemporary home with three bedrooms, two baths, and recent updates, this residence is move-in ready and awaits your personal touch.
